sellerCard.oneLiner: Expert Web Developer to Build Your Online Presence
sellerCard.description: Hi there! I'm a web developer with 6+ years of experience creating responsive websites using modern technologies. I offer custom website design, redesign, maintenance, and optimization services, and I specialize in WordPress and Shopify. Let's discuss your project requirements, and I'll provide a free consultation. Check out my portfolio for previous work samples.

description.content:
Looking for a website that's Responsive across All devices (Mobile, Desktop, Tablet) and Browsers, with clean, professional, and Fast-loading pages? You're in the right place!


I'm dedicated to delivering top-notch services, fueled by a passion for web development and design. I stay ahead of trends to ensure your site is always at its best.


WHAT YOU'LL GET:

  • Custom layout designs tailored to your business or e-commerce needs
  • A responsive website across all devices and browsers
  • Unlimited revisions until you're satisfied
  • Search engine optimization
  • Speed optimization
  • Premium WordPress themes and plugins
  • Full control over your website (easy to manage)
  • Need a business logo? I'll design a basic one for you
  • E-commerce functionality (if required)
  • Eye-catching slider and free stock images
  • Post-completion support
  • Content upload
  • Social media links integration
  • Security and backup solutions
  • A tutorial for making future edits or changes on your own


WHAT I NEED FROM YOU:

  1. Log-in info for Cpanel/Hosting/WP-admin
  2. Your content and logo
  3. A reference site (optional)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting/domain name registration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I do not provide hosting/domain name registration. In order to have comple control over the website, it is highly recommended that you purchase these yourself in your name. I recommend Bluehost and hostgator & as very reliable WordPress Hosting companies & usually there most basic package works!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I message you before placing an order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: By doing so I will be able to show you more examples of my work and more importantly, I will be able to tell you if the above packages will cover your site or if a custom quote will be needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am ready to proceed, what do I need start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It would be best if you have WordPress login credentials and a clean WP installation (can be a subdirectory). Then images and page content (brand style, texts, and anything else you will want me to use on your page). A reference or an example page (for me to understand your needs and requirements).

questionsAndAnswers.question: How to send you my Content (images, text or theme)
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please Share these all by Google drive and add your all data to that including text, images & your theme if you have any, Send me that dropbox link, and I will get it from there.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you write the content for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will not provide the content you have to provide me in a one-word file. If you don't have any issues I will add dummy content for the website design.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you provide a custom quote for my project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course! Just send me a message and lets discuss it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I see more samples of your work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Please message me. I will provide you my Portfolio.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website easily? I know just Basics.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your website will be fully editable! You will be able to very easily add text & images to all pages with a click! You will be able to edit ecommerce products, their images, descriptions & prices and add unlimited pages and posts too. No programming skills required! :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if client can't describe things in chat?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No problem we can do a meeting but it will be charged for 5 dollar order and we will do a meeting once the order is placed.
